  cmd       hexa run anima-eeg/eeg_recorder.hexa --selftest
  result    PASS — synthetic 6s split into 3×2s @ 16ch @ 250Hz, phi monotone OK
  shape     per-segment (16, 500) float32 (32128 bytes .npy v1.0)
  checks    selftest=ok / header_magic=ok / roundtrip=ok / phi_monotone=ok

