negative falsify
  segment > duration   → ABORT exit=2
  unsupported board    → ABORT exit=2
  duration <= 0        → ABORT exit=2
  segment <= 0         → ABORT exit=2
  brainflow miss       → ABORT exit=3 (hardware mode only)

